DarkMouse::

She looked up at Galvatron with a look of mock insult,"Well, I can 
try,"with a hint of sarcasm in her voice.  She was having her best 
times in front of a computer.  She punched a few buttons and scanned 
for the bot.  She found the maximal signature on the side of a 
mountain.  the hillside didn't appear to be very steep. But the 
terrane was riddled with boulders, rocks and other evedence of an 
avalance from the past winter.  She smiled and pointed to the 
signature. "That bot would be right....there."  She grinned, vary 
pleased with herself. "So, want to roll out the welcome wagon? One 
less maxmial to worry about isn't a bad idea you know. One less lazar 
shot to waste, one less bot to have to worry about dying in battle, 
one less, well the list goes on and on and on."  She sipped her cup 
of hot energon and relaxed in the chair. "So, any ideas there Boss 
bot?"
